### ==============================================
### MERCADO PAGO - WALLPAPER SALES API TESTS
### ==============================================

### 1. Crear un nuevo pago para wallpaper
POST http://localhost:7071/api/v1/payment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wallpaperNumber": 42,
  "buyerEmail": "cliente@ejemplo.com",
  "buyerName": "Juan Pérez",
  "buyerIdentificationNumber": "12345678"
}

### 2. Consultar compras por email
GET http://localhost:7071/api/v1/purchases?email=cliente@ejemplo.com

### 3. Webhook de Mercado Pago (simulación)
POST http://localhost:7071/api/v1/webhook/mercadopago
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "payment",
  "action": "payment.created",
  "data": {
    "id": "12345678901"
  },
  "live_mode": false,
  "user_id": "123456789",
  "api_version": "v1",
  "date_created": "2024-01-15T10:30:00.000Z"
}

### 4. Webhook de actualización de pago (simulación)
POST http://localhost:7071/api/v1/webhook/mercadopago
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "payment",
  "action": "payment.updated",
  "data": {
    "id": "12345678901"
  },
  "live_mode": false,
  "user_id": "123456789",
  "api_version": "v1",
  "date_created": "2024-01-15T10:35:00.000Z"
}

