### PRUEBAS DE VALIDACIÓN
### ==============================================

### 5. Crear pago con datos inválidos (email malo)
POST http://localhost:7071/api/v1/payment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wallpaperNumber": 42,
  "buyerEmail": "email-invalido",
  "buyerName": "Juan Pérez",
  "buyerIdentificationNumber": "12345678"
}

### 6. Crear pago con wallpaper number inválido
POST http://localhost:7071/api/v1/payment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wallpaperNumber": -5,
  "buyerEmail": "cliente@ejemplo.com",
  "buyerName": "Juan Pérez",
  "buyerIdentificationNumber": "12345678"
}

### 7. Crear pago con campos faltantes
POST http://localhost:7071/api/v1/payment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wallpaperNumber": 42,
  "buyerEmail": "cliente@ejemplo.com"
}

### 8. Consultar compras con email inválido
GET http://localhost:7071/api/v1/purchases?email=email-malo

### 9. Consultar compras sin email
GET http://localhost:7071/api/v1/purchases

